(55, 1, 10, 62, 1, 2, 2, 'made manifest by the appearing', 'Manifestation of Life', 'This connection highlights the theme of life being manifested through Jesus Christ. Both passages emphasize the revealing of eternal life and the abolition of death through the gospel.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
