(55, 1, 12, 65, 1, 24, 24, 'able to keep that which I have committed', 'Divine Preservation Theme', 'Both passages emphasize God''s ability to keep believers secure. 2 Timothy speaks of committing to God, while Jude assures that He can keep believers from falling.', 'theme', 0.45399999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
